Gallery - class org.eclipse.nebula.widgets.gallery.Gallery.
SWT Widget that displays an image gallery
see http://www.eclipse.org/nebula/widgets/gallery/gallery.php
This widget requires jdk-1.4+ Style VIRTUAL is used to create a Gallery whose GalleryItems are to be populated by the client on an on-demand basis instead of up-front.
